commit.title: Add support in notation for alternatives, denoted by "{|".  For example:
commit.message:
Add support in notation for alternatives, denoted by "{|".  For example:
{| opt1 | opt2 } generates an HTML box similar to that for {? ... },
containing "opt1 | opt2" but without the superscript "?".
